Package: tpca
Type: Package
Title: A function for tailoring PCA to change detection
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Author: Martin Tveten
Maintainer: Martin Tveten <matveten@gmail.com>
Description: Functionality for automatically selecting which principal components
    to keep for detecting changes in the mean and/or covariance matrix.
    The choice of principal axes to project data onto is tailored to a normal 
    state covariance matrix and a customizable distribution over relevant 
    change scenarios. Both regular PCA and dynamic PCA can be handled.
